{"id":178269,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/09/牛博编辑推荐-top-10-games-you-can’t-believe-they-made-into-movies/","date":"2011-09-09T15:01:02Z","modified":"2012-11-17T00:28:43Z","title":"牛博编辑推荐 | Top 10 Games You Can’t Believe They Made Into Movies","content":"<p><p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://img4.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/safe-x/1a-super_mario_bros.jpg\" title=\"\"><img alt=\"1a-super_mario_bros.jpg\" height=\"623\" src=\"http://img4.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/cache/112959__468x_1a-super_mario_bros.jpg\" title=\"1a-super_mario_bros.jpg\" width=\"468\" /></a></p>\n<p>The almost universally dreadful results of the 30 year history of game to movie adaptations, particularly where Hollywood is involved, are highlighted here by Japanese movie fans in this unsurprisingly abysmal ranking.</p>\n<p><span></span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.sankakucomplex.com/goto/http://cache001.ranking.goo.ne.jp/crnk/ranking/027/filmization_game/\">The ranking</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>1. Super Mario Bros.</strong></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://img4.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/safe-x/1a-super_mario_bros.jpg\" title=\"\"><img alt=\"1a-super_mario_bros.jpg\" height=\"583\" src=\"http://img4.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/cache/112959__438x_1a-super_mario_bros.jpg\" title=\"1a-super_mario_bros.jpg\" width=\"438\" /></a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://img1.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/safe-x/1b-super_mario_bros.jpg\" title=\"\"><img alt=\"1b-super_mario_bros.jpg\" height=\"293\" src=\"http://img1.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/cache/112960__438x_1b-super_mario_bros.jpg\" title=\"1b-super_mario_bros.jpg\" width=\"438\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>2. Tokimeki Memorial</strong></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://img3.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/safe-x/2-tokimeki-memorial.jpg\" title=\"\"><img alt=\"2-tokimeki-memorial.jpg\" height=\"438\" src=\"http://img3.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/cache/112961__438x_2-tokimeki-memorial.jpg\" title=\"2-tokimeki-memorial.jpg\" width=\"438\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>3. Street Fighter II</strong></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://img2.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/safe-x/3a-street-fighter.jpg\" title=\"\"><img alt=\"3a-street-fighter.jpg\" height=\"657\" src=\"http://img2.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/cache/112962__438x_3a-street-fighter.jpg\" title=\"3a-street-fighter.jpg\" width=\"438\" /></a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://img3.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/safe-x/3b-street-fighter.jpg\" title=\"\"><img alt=\"3b-street-fighter.jpg\" height=\"657\" src=\"http://img3.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/cache/112963__438x_3b-street-fighter.jpg\" title=\"3b-street-fighter.jpg\" width=\"438\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>4. Tekken</strong></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://img2.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/safe-x/4a-tekken.jpg\" title=\"\"><img alt=\"4a-tekken.jpg\" height=\"584\" src=\"http://img2.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/cache/112964__438x_4a-tekken.jpg\" title=\"4a-tekken.jpg\" width=\"438\" /></a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://img4.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/safe-x/4b-tekken.jpg\" title=\"\"><img alt=\"4b-tekken.jpg\" height=\"618\" src=\"http://img4.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/cache/112965__438x_4b-tekken.jpg\" title=\"4b-tekken.jpg\" width=\"438\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>5. Yakuza (Ryu ga Gotoku)</strong></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://img1.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/safe-x/5a-ryu-ga-gotoku.jpg\" title=\"\"><img alt=\"5a-ryu-ga-gotoku.jpg\" height=\"623\" src=\"http://img1.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/cache/112966__438x_5a-ryu-ga-gotoku.jpg\" title=\"5a-ryu-ga-gotoku.jpg\" width=\"438\" /></a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://img4.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/safe-x/5b-ryu-ga-gotoku.jpg\" title=\"\"><img alt=\"5b-ryu-ga-gotoku.jpg\" height=\"328\" src=\"http://img4.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/cache/112967__438x_5b-ryu-ga-gotoku.jpg\" title=\"5b-ryu-ga-gotoku.jpg\" width=\"438\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>6. Higurashi no Naku Koro ni</strong></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://img2.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/safe-x/6-higurashi-no-naku-koro-ni.jpg\" title=\"\"><img alt=\"6-higurashi-no-naku-koro-ni.jpg\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://img2.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/cache/112968__438x_6-higurashi-no-naku-koro-ni.jpg\" title=\"6-higurashi-no-naku-koro-ni.jpg\" width=\"438\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>7. Resident Evil</strong></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://img2.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/safe-x/7-resident-evil-1.jpg\" title=\"\"><img alt=\"7-resident-evil-1.jpg\" height=\"613\" src=\"http://img2.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/cache/112969__438x_7-resident-evil-1.jpg\" title=\"7-resident-evil-1.jpg\" width=\"438\" /></a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://img1.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/safe-x/7-resident-evil-2.jpg\" title=\"\"><img alt=\"7-resident-evil-2.jpg\" height=\"634\" src=\"http://img1.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/cache/112970__438x_7-resident-evil-2.jpg\" title=\"7-resident-evil-2.jpg\" width=\"438\" /></a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://img3.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/safe-x/7-resident-evil-3.jpg\" title=\"\"><img alt=\"7-resident-evil-3.jpg\" height=\"544\" src=\"http://img3.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/cache/112971__438x_7-resident-evil-3.jpg\" title=\"7-resident-evil-3.jpg\" width=\"438\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>8. Otogirisou</strong></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://img4.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/safe-x/8-otogirisou.jpg\" title=\"\"><img alt=\"8-otogirisou.jpg\" height=\"321\" src=\"http://img4.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/cache/112972__438x_8-otogirisou.jpg\" title=\"8-otogirisou.jpg\" width=\"438\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>9. Onechanbara</strong></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://img2.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/safe-x/9a-onechanbara.jpg\" title=\"\"><img alt=\"9a-onechanbara.jpg\" height=\"621\" src=\"http://img2.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/cache/112973__438x_9a-onechanbara.jpg\" title=\"9a-onechanbara.jpg\" width=\"438\" /></a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://img4.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/safe-x/9b-onechanbara.jpg\" title=\"\"><img alt=\"9b-onechanbara.jpg\" height=\"623\" src=\"http://img4.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/cache/112974__438x_9b-onechanbara.jpg\" title=\"9b-onechanbara.jpg\" width=\"438\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>10. Tomb Raider</strong></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://img1.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/safe-x/10-tomb-raider.jpg\" title=\"\"><img alt=\"10-tomb-raider.jpg\" height=\"651\" src=\"http://img1.sankakustatic.com/wp-content/gallery/cache/112958__438x_10-tomb-raider.jpg\" title=\"10-tomb-raider.jpg\" width=\"438\" /></a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>The worst may yet be to come – after all, blockbuster game hits like Pong, Space Invaders and Tetris still seem promisingly untapped…</p>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":994,"categories":[10466],"tags":[]}